snippet.title: Blockman 1989 Extended Trailer
snippet.description:
The official first trailer for "Blockman 1989" - coming soon to Xbox One and PC! Return as the faux retro hero, John Q. Blockman! Take to the skies! Take the cultists down! Save the ski resort! 

Music in the trailer:
Three Chain Links - "Die Historic" (found via Royalty Free Planet)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZyVq4HF8oRw

Badass Wolf Shirt - "Old Skull"
